data.description: Come see this excellent 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home located in Cibolo, TX. Built in 2013, this two-story home offers a breakfast bar, master bathroom, loft den, and a two-car garage. FULL sprinkler system, all-around gutters installed, AC and heat in the Garage and ALL APPLIANCES INCLUDED (except washer / dryer). Curtains and rods do not convey. Seller is ALSO contributing $5000 in buyer concession's which they can use towards closing costs or a interest rate buy down! This home will NOT last long! :) Act quickly!
